title: Blender is fun

<p>
I made my first animation with <a href="http://www.blender3d.org/">Blender</a> today. It just demonstrates some shadow effects. The movie is in Quicktime format using MPEG-4 compression. Quicktime 6 and the RealOne player should play it fine.
</p>
